ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of DEBORA BIELECKI of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on February 29, 2020, in the place of Wesley (Wes) Scott, whose term has expired.
